      .hgroup
        %h1 About us
        %h2
          We are creating an educational tool that teaches children to become responsible smartphone users. This tool allows parents to supervise their child’s phone activity, mitigate risks and incentivise responsible behavior.
        %ul.breadcrumb.pull-right
