            %a{:href => root_path} Home
            %span.divider /
          %li.active About us
      %article
        .row
          .span12
            %p.lead Our team are dedicated to encouraging children to communicate responsibly in the digital world. We were part of the first generation to grow up with mobile phones as young teenages and have experienced the challenges first hand.
            %p This insight has inspired us to take responsibility for this issue by practically implementing our skills and activating our passion to be a catalyst for change. We are committed to combating the cause of some of the most detrimental issues facing the youth of today – txt and cyber bullying, sexting, grooming. Not only does our team have the skills to technically develop this product, we also have advisors who are some of NZ’s leading experts in cybersafety and mobile security.
